Bumps once and for all the assemblies and installers from a project.

* Recursively fetches all files in a directory tree
* Bumps AssemblyInfo.cs [assembly: AssemblyVersion] tag
* Bumps Wix's *.wsx files for Version attribute

TFS 2010 compliant (edited files will be marked as changed), 
through the app settings.

Syntax:

- VersionBumper.exe <path of the project> major minor build revision

Sample:

- VersionBumper.exe "c:\my app" 2 0 0 8